title: Excuse Me
desc: Mobile app for people in a gathering to allow the participants to react to what is being presented
---
#### Excuse Me
* Super lightweight
* Participants in a presentation or course can queue up to ask questions or make comments
* They don't have to put their hands up and disrupt the flow
* THey don't have to get in line or ask for a mic
* Related to Classroom clicker, but much simpler.
